query:
SELECT
                v.pubdata_blob_id,
                v.proof_reveal_tx_id
            FROM
                via_votable_transactions v
            LEFT JOIN via_bridge_tx b ON b.votable_tx_id = v.id
            WHERE
                v.is_finalized = TRUE
                AND v.l1_batch_status = TRUE
                AND v.l1_batch_number = $1
                AND (
                    b.hash IS NULL
                    OR b.id IS NULL
                )
            ORDER BY
                v.l1_batch_number ASC
            LIMIT
                1
